  <!-- ABOUT -->

  <section id="about">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="reveal">
          <div id="about-img-wrap"><div class="about-img-ph" style="aspect-ratio:4/5"></div></div>
          <div class="about-quote">Every stem grown with care, from our soil to your hands.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-text">
          <p class="sec-lbl reveal rd1">Our Story</p>
          <h2 class="sec-title reveal rd2">Rooted in <em>Rhode Island</em></h2>
          <p class="about-body reveal rd3">Seven Stump Flower Farm began as a passion project in 2020 and has grown into a small-scale specialty cut flower operation tucked into the fields of Coventry, Rhode Island. What started as a love of growing has become something far more meaningful: a farm that supplies locally-grown, seasonal blooms to our community.</p>
          <p class="about-body reveal rd4">Every variety we grow is chosen with intention &mdash; for its beauty, its vase life, and the way it completes a bouquet. From the first snapdragon of spring to the last dahlia of autumn, our harvests reflect the full arc of the New England growing season.</p>
          <p class="about-body reveal rd5">We tend seven beds using sustainable practices, succession planting, and a deep belief that flowers grown close to home simply bloom better.</p>
          <div class="about-stats reveal rd6">
            <div><div class="stat-n">7</div><div class="stat-l">Growing Beds</div></div>
