          <p class="csa-body reveal rd3">Subscriptions help us plan our production, invest in seed, and grow with confidence. In return, you receive the very best of what the season offers before it ever reaches market.</p>
          <a href="#contact" class="btn-p reveal rd4" style="display:inline-block;margin-top:.5rem">Reserve Your Subscription</a>
          <p class="csa-note reveal rd5">2026 season subscriptions now open. Limited spots available.</p>
