        <div class="csa-tiers reveal rd2">
          <div class="ctier feat"><div class="cbadge">Most Popular</div><div class="ctier-head"><div class="ctname">Full Season</div><div class="ctprice">$30 <span>/ week</span></div></div><div class="ctdesc">One generous market bouquet per week, picked up at Goddard State Park Farmers Market every Friday. Runs the full growing season, May through October. First priority on specialty and limited-quantity stems.</div></div>
